    h2.section-header User Interface

    //-
        JIP Improved Recipe Menu
        Updated 2019-03-22
    //-
    +modCard('jip-improved-recipe-menu', 'JIP Improved Recipe Menu', 'https://www.nexusmods.com/newvegas/mods/59638', 'fnv-color')
        +author jazzisparis
        +version 1.20
        +installation Install JIP Improved Recipe Menu
        +notes This mod makes the crafting interface (Recipe Menu) easier, more efficient and less tedious to use.

    //-
        The Mod Configuration Menu
        Updated 2019-03-22
    //-
    +modCard('mcm', 'The Mod Configuration Menu', 'https://www.nexusmods.com/newvegas/mods/42507', 'fnv-color')
        +author Pelinor
        +version 1.5
        +installation Install The Mod Configuration Menu main file, and the MCM BugFix 2 update file
        +notes Allows any number of mods to be configured from a single menu.

    //-
        High Quality Pip-Boy Icons
        Updated 2019-03-22
    //-
    +modCard('high-quality-pip-boy-icons', 'High Quality Pip-Boy Icons', 'https://www.nexusmods.com/fallout3/mods/22808', 'fo3-color')
        +author Genin32
        +version 3.00
        +installation Install High Quality Pip-Boy Icons
        +notes This mod remasters over 100+ pip-boy icons: stats, skills, perks and apparel.

    //-
        Vanilla UI Plus
        Updated 2019-03-22
    //-
    +modCard('vanilla-ui-plus', 'Vanilla UI Plus', 'https://www.moddb.com/mods/vanilla-ui-plus/downloads', 'fnv-color')
        +author Axonis
        +version 7.71
        +installation Install Vanilla UI Plus (New Vegas) 7.71
            pre.raised
                | During setup, select Hardcore Compass
        +notes 
            | Vanilla UI Plus (VUI+) is a Fallout 3 and New Vegas mod that greatly improves the user interface without 
            | compromising the original style.
    
    //-
        Vanilla HUD Remastered
        Updated 2019-03-22
    //-
    +modCard('vanilla-hud-remastered', 'Vanilla HUD Remastered', 'https://www.nexusmods.com/newvegas/mods/64102', 'fnv-color')
        +author BmanBlazer
        +version 1.83
        +installation Install Vanilla HUD Remastered 4K v1.83
            pre.raised
                | Select VHR with VUI+ Patch. 
                | Then select Hardcore Compass. 
        +notes
            | This mod is designed to update the HUD for 1080p resolutions or higher (1440p, 4K, etc) while maintaining the
            | same original look and style. 

    //-
        UIO - UI Organizer
        Updated 2019-03-22
    //-
    +modCard('uio', 'UIO - UI Organizer', 'https://www.nexusmods.com/newvegas/mods/57174', 'fnv-color')
        +author jazzisparis
        +version 2.03
        +installation Install UIO - User Interface Organizer
        +notes 
            | An NVSE-powered plugin that is designed to manage and maintain all UI/HUD extensions added to the game by 
            | various mods. Once installed, UIO will ensure UI extensions are always properly installed and, when necessary,
            | properly removed; it will automatically detect, resolve and prevent UI-related issues, and will help keep the game's
            | UI intact. 